631
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:54,860
The worm sensed it.

632
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:56,960
That means the Golden Millet Dream's here.

633
00:36:57,430 --> 00:36:58,820
What to do?

634
00:37:00,470 --> 00:37:02,970
None but the one who shares
Ji Bozai's divine consciousness

635
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:05,300
can enter his Spirit Well.

636
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:07,740
But you're Ming Xian.

637
00:37:08,470 --> 00:37:10,006
You're literally the least likely person

638
00:37:10,030 --> 00:37:12,510
in the Six Realms to share
divine consciousness with Ji Bozai.

639
00:37:16,070 --> 00:37:17,070
Ming Xian can't do it.

640
00:37:17,200 --> 00:37:18,816
But right now you're Ming Yi,

641
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:21,380
the fairy Ji Bozai took
from Moonlit Blossoms.

642
00:37:22,550 --> 00:37:23,610
What are you getting at?

643
00:37:24,950 --> 00:37:26,130
Rules of the Six Realms.

644
00:37:26,720 --> 00:37:27,856
When you wed,

645
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:30,566
you have to form a heart imprint

646
00:37:30,590 --> 00:37:31,780
through the Marriage Stone.

647
00:37:32,200 --> 00:37:34,300
After that, you can share
divine consciousness.

648
00:37:35,070 --> 00:37:36,070
You...

649
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:39,660
You don't say.

650
00:37:40,110 --> 00:37:41,340
That's a shortcut, huh?

651
00:37:41,920 --> 00:37:42,920
Right?

652
00:37:42,950 --> 00:37:43,950
Right?

653
00:37:44,150 --> 00:37:45,150
Sounds easy enough.

654
00:37:45,680 --> 00:37:47,966
No fighting, no sparring,

655
00:37:47,990 --> 00:37:49,296
