What are you trying to say?

684
00:39:04,110 --> 00:39:05,776
Story time.

685
00:39:05,800 --> 00:39:07,740
"Chapter 13,

686
00:39:08,030 --> 00:39:09,856
Ming Yi breaking into Judgment Hall."

687
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:10,357
Come on!

688
00:39:10,381 --> 00:39:11,530
Wait!

689
00:39:12,510 --> 00:39:13,510
