701
00:39:36,320 --> 00:39:38,860
We might as well make sure
he doesn't come for nothing.

702
00:39:38,990 --> 00:39:40,296
Let's give him a surprise.

703
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:41,176
If he's here,

704
00:39:41,200 --> 00:39:43,010
