705
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:44,046
We can't hide forever,

706
00:39:44,070 --> 00:39:45,566
but at least we can hide for a while.

707
00:39:45,590 --> 00:39:47,190
Do you think I have that much time left?

708
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:49,966
Even so...

709
00:39:49,990 --> 00:39:50,990
Chapter 14.

710
00:39:51,320 --> 00:39:53,486
